%% Diagram: Retry with exponential backoff + jitter, classified by status
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Server / Storage

    C->>S: PATCH chunk (attempt 1)
    S--xC: network drop
    Note over C: wait 1s + jitter (20%)

    C->>S: PATCH (attempt 2)
    S-->>C: 503 Retry-After: 4
    Note over C: wait max(2s + jitter, 4s)

    C->>S: PATCH (attempt 3)
    S-->>C: 409 offset mismatch
    C->>S: HEAD upload (re-sync)
    S-->>C: Upload-Offset: K'
    Note over C: rebase chunk\nfrom K'

    C->>S: PATCH (attempt 4)
    S-->>C: 204 No Content
    Note over C: reset backoff window

    C->>S: PATCH next chunk
    S-->>C: 4xx (400/413/415)
    Note over C: do NOT retry\nsurface to UI
